	== 0.10.0 2023-02-10

	* Support zeitwerk 2.6.X
	
	== 0.9.0 2022-10-06

	* Use github action
	* Ruby 2.5+ needed.
	
	== 0.8.2 2022-04-23

	* Add ritual as development dependency for gem version bump
	* Update gemspec dependency.
	
	== 0.8.0 2021-11-06

	* Added: will_listen support block for hook run ruby code after code reloaded.

	== 0.7.1 2021-08-06

	* Added: add listened_folder feature, more detail, check README.md
	* Changed: Make listen wait_for_delay use default 0.1 second(1 second before).
	* Added: Add `wait_for_delay` and `listen_ignore` option to will_listen.
	* Added: add ignore options to #eager_load
	* Fixed: Listen use same logger as Zentwerk.
	* Added: Listen will ignore emacs temp files.

	== 0.6.0 2021-06-08

	* Change default logger from `method(:puts)` to a null logger.
	* Fix README.md.

	== 0.5.0 2021-06-08

	* Permit `HotReloader.will_listen` and `HotReloader.eager_load` accept a exists Zeitwerk::Loader as arg.
	* Refine Document for the process work with Roda.
